HPI 8612 Nissan Skyline GT-R 1993 JTC Suzuka 2nd Place K. Takahashi/K. Tsuchiya



Kunimitsu Takahashi & Keiichi Tsuchiya had their second best results of the 1993 JTC season finishing the Suzuka Super Touring Car 500km in 2nd place overall. Their only win for the season came in round 2 at Autopolis.
